remarks: Domination relation for restricted abstract class builders, based on a surjective function.  (Contributed by Thierry Arnoux, 27-Jan-2020.)
statement:
rabfodom.1 $e |- ( ( ph /\ x e. A /\ y = ( F ` x ) ) -> ( ch <-> ps ) ) $.
rabfodom.2 $e |- ( ph -> A e. V ) $.
rabfodom.3 $e |- ( ph -> F : A -onto-> B ) $.
rabfodom $p |- ( ph -> { y e. B | ch } ~<_ { x e. A | ps } ) $.
$d A x y $.
$d B x y $.
$d F x y $.
$d V x y $.
$d ch x $.
$d ph x y $.
$d ps y $.
